{
  "stem": "11998.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember, I was-- I was-- I was cursing the bodies, because I was-- you know, they were heavy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were sapping my-- my health, my-- my strength.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- it was terrible, because we carried them by their hands.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And their-- and their skull was bouncing along the ground.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I still remember that-- that horrible sound.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, we were there for about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they shipped us in open cars to Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going, but they shipped us out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Flossenburg is in Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went to-- and they put us about 100 people in a-- in a car, or maybe 80 people in a car, again, with two soldiers in each-- in each car.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And by about the-- they gave us a whole bread-- the whole loaf of bread, which is really four-- four days' rations.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we figure that it's going to be a long time before we're going to get food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my father and I, we cut up the bread, and we put it against our skin, underneath our shirt-- underneath our shirt.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the belt sort of held all of it around, to conceal the-- the-- the bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we wrapped it in little pieces of cloth that we carried, that we had, and so that not to lose even a crumb.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we just took a piece of bread a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And by the third day, everybody was without bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there was no water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was snowing, so we ate the snow to get some moisture.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And by about the fourth day, we could all sit.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
